reviews.review_text: The supervisor took my order at 11:20am. She told me breakfast was over, but understood when one had a craving and she got me Chicken McMuffin breakfast.  She was so polite, friendly and sweet I couldnt believe it. It was the best service I have gotten in years anywhere.  She is GOLD. THANK YOU!
Service was fast, staff was super friendly and helpful, accommodating requests whilst taking drive thru orders. A very organized team, i must say.

I had the best experience. The boy who helped me with the washroom key. The girl behind counter helped me to get drinking water. The supervisor or manager who was at Pick up area. Excellent service even when they are so busy!! Thank you!
This is the best McDonalds ever. They always get it right,  and for some reason the quality of the food is so goo,d , and it tastes so good.  Wow!
Clean and nice place! We always get our food fast no matter at drive through or on phone order!
Its McDonalds. Globally consistent and solid food. Nuggets are king.

Been here dozens of times this past year. Mostly drive through, and rarely had an issue as the orders are almost always perfect. Well maintained site inside and out, friendly and quick staff, with consistent food. I highly recommend this location.
My experience here was great. Even in the morning rush we were served swiftly. Washrooms were clean, service even came to table to ask if we wanted refills.
No one beats McDonalds.  Best fries on earth!!

Had Breakfast with my kid this morning and it was great.  The staffs were friendly and service were great too.  The manager AiL even came by later on to talk to my son and ask us how our day went.  Their dinning area are very clean.  They had an elder man cleaning and wasfriendly to everyone there too
Best location to eat outside without a pan handler asking you for money

Good Place to eat.  I love the new Chicken Big Mac.  Great Staff.  The manager Ail was great and friendly to my family especially my kids. He rewarded them each a cookies for finishing their meal. Parking: Parking is huge compare to other Restaurant. Kid-friendliness: Sad there is no playground for kids but the staffs are outstanding .  The manager name Ail was friendly and great.
Good location for a quick bite.
In Surrey for the first time from Washington and found Canadas Mcdonalds to be much better overall.

Honestly this is my most favourite McDonald s location! The workers truly value great customer service & work hard. They are always so polite and make my food fresh as well as always on time! Everytime I come I also notice them constantly cleaning/sanitizing their stations which is extremely important and needed during these difficult times. I only come to this location as I trust the workers to always give me a great experience which they already do
Visit the restaurant at lunch today.  This place is busy but every clean.  A lot of staffs working and the staffs are friendly.  Good area to dine too bad no playground area for the kids.

We went at the McDonald at 12:30 at night time to pick up the Skip order and those people were working super fast that time I went there and my order was already ready to pick up and there was a guy with the name tag of Varun I think he s the manager he was working like fire and there was a girl who was taking order she was very nice I think her name was Kulveer on the name tag and the way she was taking  order it was very nice and the girl  who was presenting at drive thru was very polite and after sometime we went there for our food it was fresh whoever was in kitchen was doing great job. we love to go back over there for sure

This location is so amazing !!! They are always very efficient and friendly. I order skip and also pick up food from them, they are always good, fast and understanding people. Whenever I get my order from other McDonald s locations, there s always a problem but these guys are so awesome specially there is a guy I think he s Mexican or middle eastern anyways he s is very nice and patient
Great service by the supervisor and staff on duty.
Fast paced. Very accommodating. The manager is a work of art! Very good at his job! Loved my experience.
Busy location but didnt have to wait too long for food even though it was served to the table. Restaurant is generally clean and pleasant to be in.
Nothing beats the view & air here! Though its a busy parking lot.  Great before/after states. Fast service.

Guy in blue shirt, who im assuming is the manager, was really hustling. Watched him multi task, bringing orders out, cleaning windows and doors, and assisting others. I got my order quickly, even though they were busy and my food was hot.
Stopped by to pick up breakfast and great service as always. Just remember to bring your own bag if you dont want to pay .25 cents for it.
Very kind, and speedy, good to visit there to eat something or pick up via drive thrugh.
The order was correct in drive thru. The girl at the cash booth named Jasmine was very sweet and polite. The presenter was very nice too.

Great quality / Great Service .5 stars but I should not eat at McDonalds simply because it is unhealthy, bad for the systems cells. But in the companies franchised beliefs and values have held up on the end. So I thank you for that. I was going to rate 3 stars because mcdonalds is bad for you, but this location has done nothing wrong in conducting a business. Respect!
Drive thru is good and havent had any mistakes yet. Theyre also usually pretty quick about the food. Inside is always nice and clean, especially since theyve renovated.

Really great experience. Maybe it was just for their 50th, but all the staff were friendly and working hard. They looked very clean and put together. The manager, Ash, was very kind and came and talked to everyone ordering their food. Very pleasant experience, and how to have it again.
Curbside pickup. The food was hot and fresh. McDonalds at its finest!
Dining area is open! The drive thru lineups take so long so its a lot faster to go inside and order using the machines or going up to the register. The staff are friendly too!

I have been going to this Mc Donald s for a while now and have never had a issue until yesterday when I got a Big Mac without the double. However after giving them a call the compensation was more than excepted. This McDonald s has in my opinion gone above and beyond.
Very fast drive through service using the app. Long lineups but moved very quickly, no wait at the windows. Just high volume.
This location s night crew is very friendly and kind. One of the manager named Varun is really nice and his night crew is awesome, they really care for people. Highly appreciated. Thanks
Very clean   customer services       I take my kids here even its far from my place  , well done

Phenomenal restaurant, I was greeted by a handsome, smart and not to be frank but sexy employee with the name tag of James at the paying window. He was super fast at taking my cash even though I gave him a hand full of pocket change he gave the rest back to me in like 10 seconds and not only that but when I got to the window I beautiful and charming girl gave me my food and off I went. Even though I live in Langley I am making this my new regular McDonalds. And also the manager Pratika needs to go.
i did dine in for about 20 mins and saw the employee sanitizing all the empty tables twice. Much appreciated that you care for the safety of the people. Thank you for your hardwork
Fries were hot at take out window.. good fast service!
All I have to say is the best staff, specially visited at around 3am. So kind and respectful, even for delivery drivers as well.

LOVE THE FOOD. HATE THE PEOPLE! PARMINDER and her staff were amazing. Myself and my three, very active boys (two of whom are autistic), came at 9-9:30am for pancakes. I had a cofee and the boys had happy meal pancakes. Parminder served our food to our table and even cleaned up after us just as we left. The boys were finished and left the table as I was tiyding up. They were loud, but not for long. They were running around. Unfortunately they do not have a play area. All this was no more than 2-5 minutes. ITS MACDONALDS!!!!!! All the GREY HAIRS did not like that. Older men and women were making comments, that I gladly replied too. One old fart even bumped into to me at the garbage can and walked away, muttering to me Assh#+e. Really? Yes that happened. Apparently cheap as dirt, SOUTH SURREY cue-tips, think MacDonalds is a place of upper class where kids cant even run around in for a brief moment. We will be back to see to staff!
Went to get restaurant today to grab my lunch and it was about amazing visit. Staffs were friendly and managers are help.  Food was hot too.
Very convenient location with a quick drive through! I get my morning coffee and the coffee is very good.

our smoothies were good but more importantly, my friends and I werent kicked out for being extremely loud and annoying. And we had alot of fun hanging out there.

There food was so good they have good customer service there for is out quick they and a drive that is really quick

Great customer service, fast and fresh food delivered always, nice staff and I love to visit this place
